                    <description>&lt;h4 id=&#34;d-prose&#34;&gt;d-Prose&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The corpus &amp;ldquo;d-Prose 1870-1920&amp;rdquo; is a heterogeneous collection of 2511 German-language literary prose texts published between 1870 and 1920. It contains narrative texts from trivial and high literature with a minimum length of 1000 words. The corpus was created from manually and semi-automatically selected texts from the German-speaking area.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Corpus: &lt;a href=&#34;https://zenodo.org/record/4315209#.X_8CsuhKhhE&#34;&gt;d-Prose&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
                
                
                
                
                
                    
                        
                    
                        
                            
                                
                                
                                
